{"tid":595594,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[估國家] 護主犬咬掉入侵者重要部份","createTime":"2018-03-16T19:18:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-19T01:48:31.000Z","uid":66324,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"4f7266bc969e9ecf0d0d4f8739640525d1a9bb8e","tid":595594,"uid":66324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T19:18:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://tribunistdaily.com/bulldog-bites-pedophiles-penis-off-as-he-tried-to-rape-sleeping-children/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftribunistdaily.com%2Fbulldog-bites-pedophiles-penis-off-as-he-tried-to-rape-sleeping-children%2F&d=dzibybXEdBHwvSxBIQK5X8n%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=943cc32e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://tribunistdaily.com/bulldog-bites-pedophiles-penis-off-as-he-tried-to-rape-sleeping-children/</a><br />\n<br />\nBULLDOG BITES PEDOPHILE&rsquo;S PENIS OFF AS HE TRIED TO RAPE SLEEPING CHILDREN<br />\n<br />\nA pedophile has been left with &ldquo;life-altering&rdquo; injuries after climbing through the bedroom window of two young children, only to be greeted by their pet bulldog who bit his penis off.<br />\n<br />\n52-year-old Randle James of Saline County, Arkansas, climbed into the 1st-floor window of the small family home into the room where the two young sisters were sleeping after passing by and seeing the open window.<br />\n<br />\nAfter climbing into the room of the 3 and 6-year-old sisters, James got more than he bargained for when family&rsquo;s Pitt Pull Terrier leaped to the girl&rsquo;s defense.The dog severed the rapist&rsquo;s genitals clean off and swallowed his penis and testicles.<br />\n<br />\nThe commotion alerted the children&rsquo;s parents who called emergency services.According to the father of the children, after calling the police, the attacker was in so much pain that he didn&rsquo;t attempt to make an escape.<br />\n<br />\nJames was rushed to the hospital where doctors treated his wounds but said they were unable to rescue his genitalia after it had been swallowed by the pet bulldog.<br />\n<br />\nHospital staff said they were able to &ldquo;patch him up,&rdquo; and while he lost a lot of blood and was clearly in a lot of pain, he would survive.<br />\n<br />\nThey added that although his injuries were no-longer life-threatening, they were &ldquo;certainly life-altering.<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;The family, who can&rsquo;t be named, said they are just thankful their dog was there to protect the young girls from the attacker.The mother of the girls said:<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;He&rsquo;s our hero. He&rsquo;ll be eating steak for a week now.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i2.wp.com/tribunistdaily.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/oiio.png?resize=768%2C460\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2.wp.com%2Ftribunistdaily.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F03%2Foiio.png%3Fresize%3D768%252C460&h=7f8d5c75&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nLocal residents described the incident, which happened around 2 am on Monday, as being &ldquo;very unusual&rdquo; for the neighborhood.<br />\n<br />\nOne neighbor said they always leave windows open at night, saying, &ldquo;we never worry about something like this happening around here.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\nAnother local resident described being awoken by the &ldquo;screaming&rdquo; during the incident:<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;I think it woke everyone in the neighborhood up.<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;I&rsquo;ve never heard anything like it.<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;Blood-curdling screams that sounded like something from a horror movie.<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;It must have lasted 20 minutes.<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;When I heard what happened I thought, &lsquo;no wonder!&rsquo;<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;Then I thought, &lsquo;good. Good doggy.&rsquo;&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\nLt. Dodson of the Saline County Sherrif&rsquo;s Office said in a statement said the family was &ldquo;lucky&rdquo; their pet was able to protect them from a potential sexual assault, adding:<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;A man entered a family home with unlawful intentions and luckily their family dog was able to prevent a serious attack from taking place.&rdquo;We are currently investigating a complaint of an attempted sexual assault and will be taking a suspect into custody as soon as he has recovered from his injuries.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\nThe dog has yet to pass the attackers genitals after swallowing them, but the family said, &ldquo;there&rsquo;s no rush; he won&rsquo;t need them now.&rdquo;"},{"pid":"c9ea7eb3542fe7e87d335284cea969e46bd85660","tid":595594,"uid":104443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T19:20:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6b36fcadcbcc4cda8e38f06365934deb00c0047","tid":595594,"uid":16208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T19:25:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf0dbeb7689d57ca7ce8b72e53b60408e434ed6d","tid":595594,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T19:25:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50f51dedbbbb2f5ee4b55934df1d8238b3e17ac8","tid":595594,"uid":62494,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T19:27:47.000Z","msg":"睇完成篇文都唔知咩國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53afb37ce03fa2f28f235fa5e8c94575fcbc5516","tid":595594,"uid":66324,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"50f51dedbbbb2f5ee4b55934df1d8238b3e17ac8","tid":595594,"uid":62494,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T19:27:47.000Z","msg":"睇完成篇文都唔知咩國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T19:28:22.000Z","msg":"Arkansas 係美國的一個州 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\